Deprecated. Replaced by FilePanelDataModel2

public class FilePanelDataModel
extends javax.swing.table.DefaultTableModel

This class allow handling of data stored in the FilePanelJTable. This class handles each row as an array of items. These items are :

  • Name
  • Size
  • Directory
  • Modified
  • Readable?
